175
00:10:14,030 --> 00:10:14,770
Claro.

176
00:10:15,950 --> 00:10:17,000
¡Koga!

177
00:10:17,950 --> 00:10:19,660
¿Quieres ir a comer yakisoba?

178
00:10:20,660 --> 00:10:22,490
Toma. Gracias.

179
00:10:26,880 --> 00:10:29,060
Oye, hermanita...

180
00:10:51,050 --> 00:10:54,450
#Sagawa

181
00:10:55,330 --> 00:10:56,910
Hola.

182
00:10:56,910 --> 00:10:58,510
¿Estabas durmiendo?

183
00:10:58,510 --> 00:11:00,650
Estaba estudiando para el ingreso, ¿sabes?

184
00:11:00,650 --> 00:11:01,650
